## Navigation Configuration

All API pages must be registered in `src/app/(pages)/docs.json` to appear in the sidebar:

<CodeSnippet language="json" title="docs.json">
{`{
  "name": "your-project",
  "navigation": {
    "tabs": [
      {
        "tab": "API Reference",
        "groups": [
          {
            "group": "Getting Started",
            "pages": [
              "api-reference/introduction",
              "api-reference/authentication"
            ]
          },
          {
            "group": "Documents",
            "pages": [
              "api-reference/documents/list",
              "api-reference/documents/create",
              "api-reference/documents/get",
              "api-reference/documents/update",
              "api-reference/documents/delete"
            ]
          },
          {
            "group": "Users",
            "pages": [
              "api-reference/users/list",
              "api-reference/users/create"
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}`}
</CodeSnippet>

**Structure:**

- **tabs**: Top-level navigation tabs
- **groups**: Sidebar sections within a tab
- **pages**: Page paths relative to `src/app/(pages)/` (without `.mdx` extension)

<Callout type="info">
Page order in the `pages` array determines the order in the sidebar and previous/next navigation links.
</Callout>

